This directory contains the chess engine JNI bridge native code.

License classification by file:
  - engine_jni.cpp: GPL v3 (partially derived from DroidFish)
      Native chmod/renice functions derived from DroidFish nativeutil.cpp.
      Copyright (C) Peter Österlund.
      JNI bridge (dlopen/dlsym/pipe) is original code.
      Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - CMakeLists.txt: AGPL v3 (original build configuration)
      Note: this CMake file builds engine_jni.cpp which is GPL v3,
      but the CMake file itself is original and uses AGPL v3.

See the root-level LICENSE-AGPL v3, LICENSE-GPL v3, and NOTICE files
for full license texts and attribution details.
